### Associate existing user account         [GET    /user-authenticate{?client_id,user_email,callback_url,state}]
If the user already exists in CogniFit, their account can be associated. Redirect the user to this 
end point. If the user accepts to associate the CogniFit accout with the partner, the user_token will be
sent back to the callback_url provided. The callback_url must be one of the callback urls
communicated to CogniFit when the partner was created.

State parameter is a hash generated by the partner. This value will be added to the callback response.


+ Parameters
    + client_id: 906354cf409c859a01053e29effc283ffc283fdr - (string 40)
