## Associates registration                  [/registration/new-associate/register]

It is possible, through the API, to create client accounts under the main client account. This process will generate distinct credentials for each client account. 

You can then make requests to every endpoint with the main credentials and add an extra parameter in the body called 'alternative_identity.' All requests made will be consolidated under the main client account. 

You must request <a href="mailto:integration@cognifit.com">integration@cognifit.com</a> to enable this functionality for your account.

